# XGBoost Activation — Phase 1 Walkthrough

## What Was Done

Closed 4 critical gaps in the ML data pipeline that were preventing XGBoost from ever training. The pump prediction model was 100% dormant despite being wired into Agent 5's scoring logic.

## Root Causes Found

| Gap | Impact |
|---|---|
| `feature_builder.save()` used relative path `src/ml/data` | Features never saved to disk — resolves wrong depending on working directory |
| `MLTrainer.save_outcome()` never called | No trade outcomes recorded → trainer can't label training data |
| No retraining job in scheduler | Even with data, model would never retrain |
| `_trade_id` missing from feature vectors | Trainer couldn't match features to outcomes |

