### [feature_builder.py](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive/Desktop/projects/Crypto-trading-bot/backend/src/ml/feature_builder.py)
- `build()` now accepts `trade_id` parameter, embeds as `_trade_id` in feature dict
- `save()` now defaults to absolute path (`os.path.dirname(__file__)/data`) instead of relative `src/ml/data`

